    "• The study offers further confirmation of the robustness of TA in the novel context of wholesale adoption of large language models.",
    "• Our study shows the modulation of the relationships between the factors of Unified Theory of Acceptance and Use of Technology (UTAUT) in the novel context, that is, we find no significant relationship between Effort Expectancy (EE) and Behavioral Intentions (BI).",
